name: Tropical Rainforest Apocalypse
description: This is the situation and condition of the tropical rain forest in my beloved country. All trees are cut down, cleared for oil palm plantations and coal mining. Floods in Kalimantan is an unnatural thing in long time history. Previously, forests and mountains were also burned due to global warming. The world's oxygen reserves are running low, because his lungs are being cut off. And now the motherland is always crying. Earthquakes, volcanoes eruption, floods, and occur in almost every corner of my beloved country.
